source: Allows you to build or set up integrations which subscribe to certain events on Open Social
Exposes user account events as webhooks.
Exposes user login events as webhooks.
When a user accesses the site for the first time, this is counted as a first login.
When a user registers or is added to the to the platform, this webhook is triggered.
When a user sets a password for the first time this webhook is triggered. This only occurs when the user did not register via Open Social but an external service.
